"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640904098,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"xPu3DWpjLlQIyQHq6_96BvBP9TxkdGSCaNOz7AoSRlM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x13f0A814965AD981813f7E79a2387839DB4eacb3\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"IFDPK4wBl_6hf6OF-v3X-NmE0DJT7MpH5GuonUnztJ4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"wvQEHw4FGRbWkp-MhDCKR-fMxvM9WSfawXYWSA9W4rQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"lWx_1DiVtg0E3XCVjgxqFG4uCVhJT9EknjIsJ33uzd4JZrIWOOE3mH8zJAaDVB8UZ3IGCH7ULF261pErZrkpWw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x095ff9d43af7d4337878167a13f145cb6d8deeaa8821ce4c7a233b68f76d126c43214c8dc1ab93f2d0cd792c10da234d759fc2edb029dda7719871853b8086a81c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"IFDPK4wBl_6hf6OF-v3X-NmE0DJT7MpH5GuonUnztJ4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"wvQEHw4FGRbWkp-MhDCKR-fMxvM9WSfawXYWSA9W4rQ\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi